/-- A category `C` `IsSifted` if
1. the diagonal functor `C ⥤ C × C` is final.
2. there exists some object. -/
class IsSifted : Prop extends IsSiftedOrEmpty C where
  [nonempty : Nonempty C]

/- This instance is scoped since
